main event: A bright object was sighted over a field in Delavan, Wisconsin, moving fast to the east.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for 1-2 minutes,The object was described as small and round, approximately eight feet in diameter,The object appeared to be spinning and flickering on and off,Observation was made from the ground by a civilian,No unusual activity or air traffic was reported in the area at the time of the sighting.
